      • scheduleBackendFeedback

        public static void scheduleBackendFeedback(java.lang.Integer backendId,
                                           VideoList videos,
                                           java.lang.Long taskId)
        Create and schedule the task for all capable back-ends included in the task designated by the task Id. The given back-end Id will not participate in the feedback task.
        Parameters:
        backendId - the back-end that send the task finished call, this back-end is automatically omitted from the list of target back-ends
        videos - videos returned in task finished call
        taskId - the id of the finished analysis task
